des:
The Golf Flash Briefing brings you the latest news about what is happening in the world of golf. Presented by Bladed Wedge.

Bladed Wedge is the spot to stay up to date on the world of golf. The opinionated/social media approach is different from traditional golf sites and lets you follow golf in a more casual/fun way. Check out our latest blogs at www.bladed-wedge.com or catch our updates here!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
